name: Gibi ASMR
description:
Gibi is a YouTuber who is mainly known for making ASMR, which is a genre of videos about sounds and e-girls. She also streams on twitch and does cosplay.

The embed has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models. Seems to tend the variety of clothing on some models, but increasing the token weight or using inpainting helps out.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)
